uls-desc: Sõngda ned sẽn dat n bãng buud-gomd ning a sẽn dat n togsã
ext-uls-undo-language-tooltip-text-local: Buud-gomda toeemame ne wiki kada. Ges-y y [[Special:GlobalPreferences|global preferences]] n  toeem wiki wã buud-gomd fãa pʋgẽ.
uls-betafeature-desc: Wilg-y buud-gomd nins sẽn be sebr-sodga pʋge,sen ya sõma n yɩɩda-yã
ext-uls-display-settings-desc: Sõng-y n ges buud-gomd ning b sẽn tũnugd ne menusã la fõntã.
ext-uls-language-buttons-help: Yãk-y n toeem y sõssã goam. Sõng-kãngã pa na n sãam bũmb nins sẽn be Biiblã pʋgẽ wã ye.
ext-uls-display-settings-anon-log-in-cta: [[Special:UserLogin|kẽ]] sing-ya n yãk buud-gomd a to.
ext-uls-webfonts-settings-info: Tak-y gʋls-biise ninse m menme la-y yaool yãk y gʋls-bɩɩs nins yãm rata
ext-uls-webfonts-select-for-ui-info: Gʋls-bɩɩse n toe tʋm ne intefɛse
ext-uls-input-settings-ui-language: Gomde ning b sẽn tũnugd ne b sɛbã pʋgẽ
ext-uls-input-settings-noime: Kẽesgo soy-ramba ka be ne gomd kada.
ext-uls-input-disable-notification-info-: Y tõe n kɩtame tɩ b tool-rãmbã kẽ wakat fãa, y sẽn dat n bãng buud-gomdã pʋgẽ wã.
Y tõe n kɩtame tɩ tʋʋm-teed-ramba kẽ wakat ning fâa buud-gomd malgra n nan pʋg gomde-sebr
ext-uls-compact-link-info: buud-goam fãa (yẽ ne neb a taab sẽn yãk b toorẽ buud-goamy n sɩng b baoorã)
ext-uls-compact-language-links-preferenc: Tʋm ne [[$1 sẽn yaa buud-gomd sõdg sebr]], ne buud-goam sẽn yaa sõma ne yãmba.
ext-uls-compact-no-results: Neng kada ka be buud-gomdã pʋgẽ ne baoba ye.
ext-uls-setlang-error: Y sẽn da nong n dat n gom buud-gomdã, y paama yel-wẽnd n paasdẽ. Yʋsg: $1
ext-uls-setlang-message: Y sẽn tũ-yã linkã kosa taab n wilg tɩ y na n paama sõsg ne $1 ($2)
ext-uls-setlang-heading: Y tõe n toeema intɛface buud-gomde?
ext-uls-empty-state-header-actions-avail: Buud-goam ka be ye. Y na paas paalga ye?
ext-uls-empty-state-desc-actions-availab: Maane gʋlsg y buud-goama wʋsgo ka pʋga
